title: Wholesale Price of Window Glass, American, Single for New York
notes:
Series Is Presented Here As Two Variables--(1)--Original Data, 1890-1933 (2)--Original Data, 1933-1942. The Bls Bulletins On Wholesale Prices For 1933 And 1934 Misprint The Data For 1933 And July, 1934. Therefore, Data Were Copied From Corresponding Series In NBER Files. Bls Wholesale Prices Bulletins Were Published Semiannually After July, 1935. Source: Bls Bulletins

This NBER data series m04078b appears on the NBER website in Chapter 4 at http://www.nber.org/databases/macrohistory/contents/chapter04.html.
